Thank you for reading and learning more about what we will be providing here 🚀🪐

- With the power of community and skilled team members, we can communally learn how to analyze trending projects with popular tools, and develop a deeper understanding of the nft and crypto space and project strategy as a whole.

5) We are planning to provide alpha through a signals channel & an alpha category, hosting nightly "degen hour" sessions in vcs, as well as holding alpha events and providing exclusive channels to holders for following nft/crypto news, and popular watchlists.

- These AMAs will provide insight into upcoming projects and a deeper look into the founders of these projects
- We will be providing WL spots for partnered projects and release these spots to holders of Cosmiqs through giveaways!

4) We see partnerships with other projects as a great opportunity to provide value to our community here, so instead of only gathering WL spots to distribute, we plan on collaborating with projects and hosting weekly AMAs with founders as well as influencers that we partner with.
-We want to work hands on with members of our community and know that we can provide a platform for you to make life changing connections and get valuable advice from our skilled team.
- The master classes, community events, founder events, and advisement sessions are some ways we will be providing a platform for holders to grow and learn together.
3) Our utility is based on our passion for growing the members of our community with unique skillsets and passion to learn.
- VIP Members holding more than 2 Cosmiqs are prioritized for WL distribution, our weekly eth giveaways, as well as priority in decision making for future ventures.

- We appreciate those members who take pride in the beautiful artwork of our collection while holding 2 or more Cosmiqs, we want to provide benefits to those members with an exclusive "VIP" role that will provide further utility inside the Discord.
2) An important topic we covered in our AMA was VIP holder benefits. Members who hold 2 or more Cosmiqs will have exclusive access to more hands on founder experiences.

-We wanted to prioritize community building first, and physical/other utilities after. However, our strategic use of a large admin wallet will provide us with opportunities to invest into physical goods as well as digital ventures.

1) Our roadmap is community focused, but we do have a large admin wallet allocation of revenue that will be used to re-invest into the project's physical ventures, and further utilities down the line.
